snippet.title: Gran Turismo® 5 E3 2010 Trailer
snippet.description:
Enjoy the brand new Gran Turismo® 5 trailer from E3, with exclusive never-before-seen footage of some of the 950+ vehicles and licensed and fictional tracks from the game, and get a sneak peek at what's to come in Gran Turismo® 5.

http://us.gran-turismo.com/us/
